This is the [talk page](/Wikipedia:Talk_page_guidelines) dedicated to discussing proposed improvements to the [War on drugs](/War_on_drugs) article, functioning as a collaborative workspace where editors can propose edits, raise questions, and seek consensus on contentious issues while adhering to Wikipedia’s editorial standards.  

This is [not a forum](/Wikipedia:What_Wikipedia_is_not) for general discussion of the subject of the article; rather, it is a focused venue for encyclopedic improvement, policy clarification, and sourcing debates directly related to the [War on drugs](/War_on_drugs) entry.  

